	<Title>
		Do your sunglasses get the job done?
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Sunglasses are more than a fashion statement. When you&apos;re shopping for shades, skip sunglasses that are labeled &quot;cosmetic&quot; or that don&apos;t offer details about UV protection. Instead look for sunglasses that provide at least 99 percent protection from UVA and UVB light.&lt;/p&gt;
